@startuml snapshot_management
title Snapshot: Save / List / Diff / Restore / Delete

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Evolution" as bausteinsicht_cli_evolution
participant "Snapshot" as bausteinsicht_snapshot

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 1. bausteinsicht snapshot save ‑‑label pre-refactor
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_snapshot : 2. capture current model.jsonc + metadata
bausteinsicht_snapshot --> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 3. written to .bausteinsicht-snapshots/
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 4. bausteinsicht snapshot list
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_snapshot : 5. read snapshot index
bausteinsicht_snapshot --> architect : 6. labeled snapshots, newest first
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 7. bausteinsicht snapshot diff pre-refactor ‑‑against current
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_snapshot : 8. load snapshot + current model, compute delta
bausteinsicht_snapshot --> architect : 9. added / removed / changed elements
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 10. bausteinsicht snapshot restore pre-refactor (destructive: overwrites model.jsonc)
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_snapshot : 11. delete: remove a labeled snapshot

@enduml
